FAQ’s

What is psychometric testing and why is it necessary for startups? It is an innovative technique that is being used for measuring candidates’ cognitive abilities, personality traits, and behavioral patterns. It provides a solution to startups by selecting an individual who has the right skills and also conforms to the cultural touchpoint of an organization, thereby minimizing hiring risks and enhancing team composure.
What does Think Exam offer to startups in terms of psychometric testing? Think Exam is a user-friendly platform where the psychometric tests can be organized. Provides custom-made assessments depending on the requirements of a particular role, has data-driven insights, supports scalable solutions in growing startups.
Will Think Exam be able to customize itself for every role in a startup? The answer is yes. It is able to customize the psychometric test by the values and required specializations for every role rendering them applicable to the specific culture and objectives of the organization.
Can Think Exam adapt itself with the growth of a startup? Yes, for small teams or across rapid shifts of the business, an adaptable solution is provided by Think Exam, which comprehensively matches itself with the growth of a startup.
